{"id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0001","text":"像一齣戲緊張刺激 哀怨也迷離","structure":{"line_index":1,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["戲劇性","情感糾葛","懸疑"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["戲","緊張","刺激","哀怨","迷離"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,3,3,4,9,3,4,3,3,4,5,0,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zoeng6","jat1","ceot1","hei3","gan2","zoeng1","ci3","gik1","oi1","jyun3","jaa5","mai4","lei4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"像","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"一齣戲","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"緊張","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"刺激","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"哀怨","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"也","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"迷離","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"以戲劇比喻情感的起伏與不明朗，語氣帶有懸念。"},"source":{"title":"不再分離","artists":["葉德嫺"],"lyricists":["潘源良"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2021","prev_line_id":null,"next_line_id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0002","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0002","text":"幾經喜與悲分隔開 竟再相聚跟你一起","structure":{"line_index":2,"char_count":16},"semantics":{"themes":["分離","重逢","情感的循環"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["喜","悲","分隔","相聚","一起"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[9,3,9,5,3,3,4,3,9,4,2,3,5,3,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["gei2","ging1","hei2","jyu5","bei1","fan1","gaak3","hoi1","ging2","zoi3","zeoi6","gan1","nei5","jat1","hei2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"幾經","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"喜","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"與","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"悲分","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"隔開","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"竟","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"再","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"相聚","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"跟","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"一起","pos":"PART"}],"syntax_notes":"描述經歷了情感的起伏後，再次相遇的喜悅。"},"source":{"title":"不再分離","artists":["葉德嫺"],"lyricists":["潘源良"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2021","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0001","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0003","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0003","text":"捉不住的姻緣 曾令我差點跌下不可再起","structure":{"line_index":3,"char_count":17},"semantics":{"themes":["命運","失落","絕望"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["姻緣","跌下","不可再起"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,3,2,3,3,0,0,2,5,3,9,4,2,3,9,4,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zuk1","bat1","zyu6","dik1","jan1","jyun4","cang4","ling6","ngo5","caa1","dim2","dit3","haa6","bat1","ho2","zoi3","hei2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"捉","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"不住","pos":"PART"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"姻緣","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"曾令","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"差點","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"跌下","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"不可","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"再起","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"感嘆命運的捉弄，曾一度陷入低谷，幾乎無法翻身。"},"source":{"title":"不再分離","artists":["葉德嫺"],"lyricists":["潘源良"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2021","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0002","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0004","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0004","text":"誰料那天路中燈下人散處 你竟等我再見你","structure":{"line_index":4,"char_count":18},"semantics":{"themes":["意外","重逢","緣分"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["路中","人散","等我","再見"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,5,3,2,3,3,2,0,9,5,9,9,5,4,4,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["seoi4","liu6","naa5","tin1","lou6","zung1","dang1","haa6","jan4","saan2","nei5","ging2","dang2","ngo5","zoi3","gin3","nei5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"誰料","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"那天","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"路","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"中燈","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"下","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"人","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"散處","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"竟","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"等","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"再見","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"描述在意外的時刻，於人潮中重逢的驚喜與等待。"},"source":{"title":"不再分離","artists":["葉德嫺"],"lyricists":["潘源良"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2021","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0003","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0005","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0005","text":"是愛着你但不想碰運氣","structure":{"line_index":5,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["愛戀","謹慎","對未來的擔憂"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["愛着","不想","碰運氣"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,4,2,5,2,3,9,4,2,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["si6","oi3","zoek6","nei5","daan6","bat1","soeng2","pung3","wan6","hei3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"是","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"愛","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"着","pos":"PART"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"但","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"不想","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"碰運氣","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"表達愛意，但因過去的經歷而對關係的發展感到猶豫。"},"source":{"title":"不再分離","artists":["葉德嫺"],"lyricists":["潘源良"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2021","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0004","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0006","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0006","text":"然後讓我在這燈下欄柵處","structure":{"line_index":6,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["等待","重逢的場景","承諾"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["讓","燈下","欄柵"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,2,5,2,5,3,2,0,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jin4","hau6","joeng6","ngo5","zoi6","ze5","dang1","haa6","laan4","caak3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"然後","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"讓","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"在","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"這燈","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"下","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"欄柵","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"處","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"描繪重逢的具體地點，暗示著一個重要的時刻。"},"source":{"title":"不再分離","artists":["葉德嫺"],"lyricists":["潘源良"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2021","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0005","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0007","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0007","text":"說一千次我愛你","structure":{"line_index":7,"char_count":7},"semantics":{"themes":["愛意的表達","情感的累積"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["說","一千次","我愛你"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[4,3,3,4,5,4,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["syut3","jat1","cin1","ci3","ngo5","oi3","nei5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"說","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"一千次","pos":"NUM"},{"text":"我愛你","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"以誇張的次數強調愛意的深厚與渴望表達。"},"source":{"title":"不再分離","artists":["葉德嫺"],"lyricists":["潘源良"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2021","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0006","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0008","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0008","text":"不想追究到底那天 怎會說別離 但總想說聲","structure":{"line_index":8,"char_count":18},"semantics":{"themes":["過去的傷痛","和解的渴望","情感的釋放"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["追究","別離","說聲"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,9,3,4,4,9,5,3,9,4,2,0,2,9,9,4,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["bat1","soeng2","zeoi1","gau3","dou3","dai2","naa5","tin1","zam2","syut3","bit6","lei4","daan6","zung2","soeng2","syut3","sing1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"不想","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"追究","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"到底","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"那天","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"怎會","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"說","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"別離","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"但","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"總想","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"說聲","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"表達不想深究過去的分離原因，但渴望表達情感。"},"source":{"title":"不再分離","artists":["葉德嫺"],"lyricists":["潘源良"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2021","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0007","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0009","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0009","text":"親愛的請你今後跟我一起 講不盡的癡情","structure":{"line_index":9,"char_count":17},"semantics":{"themes":["承諾","愛情的永恆","深情"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["親愛的","今後","一起","癡情"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,4,3,9,5,3,2,3,5,3,9,9,3,2,3,3,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["can1","oi3","dik1","cing2","nei5","gam1","hau6","gan1","ngo5","jat1","hei2","gong2","bat1","zeon6","dik1","ci1","cing4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"親愛","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"請","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"今後","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"跟","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"一起","pos":"PART"},{"text":"講","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"不盡","pos":"PART"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"癡情","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"直接向對方表達愛意與長久的承諾，充滿深情。"},"source":{"title":"不再分離","artists":["葉德嫺"],"lyricists":["潘源良"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2021","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0008","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0010","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0010","text":"留在我的心窩裏面總不會死","structure":{"line_index":10,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情的堅定","永恆的承諾","內心的歸屬"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["留在","心窩","不會死"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,5,3,3,3,5,2,9,3,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["lau4","zoi6","ngo5","dik1","sam1","wo1","leoi5","min6","zung2","bat1","sei2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"留在","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"心窩","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"裏面","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"總","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"不會","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"死","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"強調愛意永存於心，不會因時間或距離而消逝。"},"source":{"title":"不再分離","artists":["葉德嫺"],"lyricists":["潘源良"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2021","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0009","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0011","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0011","text":"然而若你又匆匆地離棄我","structure":{"line_index":11,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["擔憂","害怕失去","關係的不確定性"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["然而","匆匆","離棄"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,0,2,5,2,3,3,2,0,4,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jin4","ji4","joek6","nei5","jau6","cung1","cung1","dei6","lei4","hei3","ngo5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"然而","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"若","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"又","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"匆匆","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"地","pos":"PART"},{"text":"離棄","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"表達對對方可能再次離開的擔憂與不安。"},"source":{"title":"不再分離","artists":["葉德嫺"],"lyricists":["潘源良"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2021","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0010","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y-25b635ai0_MjAyMQ_0012","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
